.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-CLOSE-EXPIRED-INVOICES" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-close-expired-invoices \- delete all expired unpaid invoices
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-close-expired-invoices
.SH DESCRIPTION
Finds all unpaid invoices past their expiry time and deletes them via
.BR delinvoice .
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"deleted":N, "total_expired":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-list-expired (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-expire (1)
